import {Component, HostBinding, Input, OnInit} from '@angular/core';
import {Router} from '@angular/router';
import {animate, state, style, transition, trigger} from '@angular/animations';
import { NavItem } from './nav-item';
import { AuthenticationService } from '../../_services';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-menu-list-item',
  templateUrl: './menu-list-item.component.html',
  styleUrls: ['./menu-list-item.component.css'],
  animations: [
    trigger('indicatorRotate', [
      state('collapsed', style({transform: 'rotate(0deg)'})),
      state('expanded', style({transform: 'rotate(180deg)'})),
      transition('expanded <=> collapsed',
        animate('225ms cubic-bezier(0.4,0.0,0.2,1)')
      ),
    ])
  ]
})
export class MenuListItemComponent implements OnInit {
  @Input()
  isToggleEnabled:boolean;
  expanded: boolean;
  @HostBinding('attr.aria-expanded') ariaExpanded = this.expanded;
  @Input() item: NavItem;
  @Input() drawer:any;
  @Input() depth: number;
  constructor(public router: Router, private authenticationService: AuthenticationService) {
    if (this.depth === undefined) {
      this.depth = 0;
    }
  }

  ngOnInit() {
    // this.navService.currentUrl.subscribe((url: string) => {
    //   if (this.item.route && url) {
    //     // console.log(`Checking '/${this.item.route}' against '${url}'`);
    //     this.expanded = url.indexOf(`/${this.item.route}`) === 0;
    //     this.ariaExpanded = this.expanded;
    //     // console.log(`${this.item.route} is expanded: ${this.expanded}`);
    //   }
    // });
  }

  onItemSelected(item: NavItem, drawer:any) {


    if(item.loginRequired && !this.authenticationService.isLoggedIn()) {
      this.router.navigate(['/login']);
      return;
    }

    if (!item.children || !item.children.length) {
      if(this.isToggleEnabled)
         drawer.toggle();
      this.router.navigate([item.route]);
      // this.navService.closeNav();
    }
    if (item.children && item.children.length) {
      this.expanded = !this.expanded;
    }
  }
}

<a mat-list-item [ngStyle]="{'padding-left': (depth * 12) + 'px'}" (click)="onItemSelected(item, drawer)"
   [ngClass]="{'active': item.route ? router.isActive(item.route, true): false, 'expanded': expanded}"
   class="menu-list-item">
  <mat-icon class="routeIcon">{{item.iconName}}</mat-icon>
  {{item.displayName}}
  <span fxFlex *ngIf="item.children && item.children.length">
    <span fxFlex></span>
    <mat-icon style="margin-top:8px"  [@indicatorRotate]="expanded ? 'expanded': 'collapsed'">
      expand_more
    </mat-icon>
  </span>
</a>
<div *ngIf="expanded">
  <app-menu-list-item *ngFor="let child of item.children" [item]="child" [drawer] = "drawer" [isToggleEnabled] = "isToggleEnabled" [depth]="depth+1">
  </app-menu-list-item>
</div>
